Hi, player!
This game is called Bouncy.

Your task is to break all the bricks in each level.
Breaking bricks gives you points.
Right mouse click makes the ball move.
Use the paddle to guide the ball
by moving your mouse left and right.
Some bricks release boosts.
Red boosts are negative and green ones positive.
Catching red boosts lowers your score.
Green boosts increase your score.

Make sure to get the high score!
Good luck!